      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained throughout its ownership. The engine runs smoothly, and the transmission shifts reliably, making it a dependable choice for any driver. While the exterior looks great overall, there are some minor rock chips on the hood and small door dings that are typical for a car of this age. Inside, the cabin is clean and comfortable, though you will find some light wear on the driver's seat bolster and minor fading on a few dashboard buttons. All major electronics and safety features are fully functional. It\u2019s a solid, honest car that is ready for its next owner without needing immediate repairs.",
