    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my reliable ride, and it\u2019s honestly been such a joy to own. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-cared for over the years. Everything runs just like it should, making it the perfect choice if you're looking for something dependable and ready to hit the road today. I\u2019d love for it to go to a good home\u2014come check it out and take it for a spin!",
