    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine and a desirable 6-speed longitudinal manual transmission. This example boasts a linear power delivery via its individual throttle bodies and maintains excellent compression across all cylinders. Critical maintenance has been addressed, including a comprehensive VANOS system overhaul and proactive rear subframe reinforcement to ensure chassis integrity under high lateral loads. The suspension retains its factory-spec geometry with refreshed bushings, providing the tactile hydraulic steering feedback these cars are known for. While the exterior reflects its status as a well-loved driver's car, the drivetrain and limited-slip differential are dialed in for immediate performance.",
      "price": 32500.0,
