    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle strikes the perfect balance between luxury and daily utility. The exterior retains a deep, glossy finish, showing only minor signs of careful use consistent with a well-loved car. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary; the premium upholstery is supple and free of tears, while every button, dial, and digital display functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, this car is turn-key ready. It has benefited from a rigorous preventative maintenance schedule, including recent fluid flushes and a set of high-quality tires with ample tread remaining. The engine runs quietly at idle and delivers smooth, responsive power on the highway, complemented by a transmission that shifts seamlessly through every gear. With no warning lights, no leaks, and a smoke-free interior, this is a reliable, complete package for a buyer who values a car that has been treated with genuine respect.",
      "price": 34500.0,
